      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Apple Smoothie with Raspberries. An American family-table recipe, generous, comforting, built for a crowd. Adjustable for what you need.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "In and out of the blender in under five minutes. A frozen banana does most of the texture work.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
